{"tid":2137773,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《頭條動新聞》Ep.1  (蘋果日報 Appledaily)","createTime":"2020-08-03T07:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T07:34:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d5902badeb35341a9baf802a1561aacd3d2ecc6e","tid":2137773,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:34:15.000Z","msg":"#王喜 #頭條動新聞 #Appledaily<br />\n<br />\n《頭條動新聞》Ep.1 <br />\n(蘋果日報 Appledaily)<br />\nAug 3, 2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6QfHyCq45j4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6QfHyCq45j4&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=7d294316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6QfHyCq45j4</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果動新聞 HK Apple Daily<br />\n1.68M subscribers<br />\n<br />\n面對強權打壓，批判政府的聲音越來越少，《頭條動新聞》請來《四點鐘王Sir》主持王喜，以及《AppleDaily Show豪》主持曾志豪，繼續與香港人一同嬉笑怒罵、諷刺時弊。如你想支持《頭條動新聞》兩位創作人曾志豪和王喜，可於YouTube收看節目直播期間，按留言位右邊的按鈕，選擇購買「Super Sticker」，或以自由定價的「超級即時通訊」作支持。扣除成本後將全數撥歸合作夥伴，與你攜手撐同路人！<br />\n<br />\n  《四點鐘王Sir》  <br />\n過去一年防暴警執勤其間多次「仆街」，王Sir從裝備上及心理上以至身理上的狀況，詳細解構總總成因，以及在《警察通例》下如何可作出糾正。<br />\n<br />\n《AppleDaily Show豪》<br />\n市民踎街食飯一日後撤回堂食禁令，撤回速度遠勝5個月才願意收回「逃犯條例」，除撤回速度快，DQ速度更快，一連串立會參選人被DQ後，林鄭更將整個選舉徹底DQ，原來《基本法》已成為宗教。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 ： <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=c299e26f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&h=bbd68420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com</a><br />\n即 like 蘋果 fb  ： <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=899775e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia</a><br />\niPhone App ：